text: Nemaschema flavovittatum is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1976.BioLib.cz - Nemaschema flavovittatum. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1976
